{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":10,"day":2}],"page_start":6,"page_end":6,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"毛主席，各族人民永远忠于您","authors":["彝族","普正光"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金沙江水清又清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民心向北京城。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京城，太阳升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席登上天安门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七亿人民齐欢腾。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席领导我们闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒奴隶主得翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑暗的世界放光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦变甜，不忘本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远跟着伟大领袖毛泽东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"条条道路通北京，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席和各族人民心连心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心连心，一条心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席是咱们知心人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的话句句是真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民听了都执行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年万载不变心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族人民永远忠于您。"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}